HEADWORD: Ravener
<hw>Rav"en*er</hw> <pr>(r⟦acr⟧v"'n*⟦etil⟧r)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<sn>1.</sn> <def>One who, or that which, ravens or plunders.</def>
